{"tid":316863,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同男友北上按摩，嬲左佢成日","createTime":"2017-07-11T05:13:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T06:07:36.000Z","uid":82845,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9a73a6fb1e90966c3cb3fe35da48e05e1e443f96","tid":316863,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:13:01.000Z","msg":"同男友二人北上按摩 揀左間 之前同兩個朋友（情侶）都去過一次 ---水Ｘ雲Ｘ<br />\n我同過佢講 推油網上好似話會推埋個春袋<br />\n之後按完大堂送既按腳之後<br />\n佢自己行左去搵人 話安排上房<br />\n點知返到黎 佢話做泰式<br />\n我話做中式<br />\n佢話咁我上房先 佢話冇房<br />\n咁我自己上房做中式啦<br />\n咁佢做完都過左黎我間房搵我 過夜<br />\n咁佢要求叫我比$600佢 聽朝埋單咁d錢佢既<br />\n我只不過係 幫佢袋住 我問點解<br />\n佢話 係你個袋拎 好似好肉酸咁<br />\n咁好啦 安排好聽日既行程之後 就訓教<br />\n第二朝大家沖完涼換好衫就去大堂<br />\n咁我出去先既  個服務員比左張單我<br />\n<br />\n我望一望 唔L係啊 張單顯示 一項服務叫魅力激情 仲要$279　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我即刻呆左 個腦就諗起好多淫亂既畫面<br />\n之後佢就發返我脾氣 叫我入去問清楚 唔係就話我周圍唱<br />\n我摸不著頭腦 有咩好唱？ 同埋我入去問乜野?<br />\n如果普通推油 點解唔一齊係同一間房做<br />\n點解要呃我 同我講話做泰式<br />\n其實係咪唔應該再一齊？我好想知到底做過d乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e16261249e655371263a58625380c0143704356e","tid":316863,"uid":15473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:18:10.000Z","msg":"正常野"},{"pid":"9c6907ecc5c786be18920b558cc376c11f6cdf69","tid":316863,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f18a34ee3f824fa33ba0a8a3d7146093c16e083","tid":316863,"uid":3117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:18:45.000Z","msg":"垃圾假膠 作都作好d啦 1999"},{"pid":"5f4b4dead95bef3dbf8f759f37da5d9e339e012e","tid":316863,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:19:52.000Z","msg":"互射返幾劑發洩下囉"},{"pid":"fc636aeca974e12d87154a4c88d7794bb1dcb26d","tid":316863,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:21:53.000Z","msg":"再嘈就飛撚左你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682374abaf70456bed568f5eb9f913eba1f8d3f5","tid":316863,"uid":52819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:23:55.000Z","msg":"如果邪野 聽講張單唔會寫出黎喎"},{"pid":"64cd02f28ececd7cfbfbbf6212627c1058a82182","tid":316863,"uid":88805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:24:44.000Z","msg":"on 99, 打文打到1999, 成篇逗號都冇個"},{"pid":"b35bd4e64751a1ec2e4e9c42b901df8709570d67","tid":316863,"uid":93882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T06:00:01.000Z","msg":"呢間野之前黃曬啦！"},{"pid":"75de02cb83c54957dff2c257cdf293a0342c2680","tid":316863,"uid":51348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T06:02:57.000Z","msg":"屌語癌咪岀post啦"},{"pid":"eef6f0743b451cb5a8ae3629d7a5d3c4957895cb","tid":316863,"uid":4155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T06:03:36.000Z","msg":"推油係泰式大床，中式係細床<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n魅力激情要俾3舊tips先有野玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee76f20926b99b18561b4fe610e3b66f001c937c","tid":316863,"uid":17642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T06:07:36.000Z","msg":"港式得啦"}]}